comments: Poole (GSW) slides his hand off Grant's (POR) body during the layup attempt, and the contact is marginal.
Thompson (GSW) is jumping across Grant's (POR) path with vertical arms as he contests the shot attempt.
Watford (POR) makes incidental foot-to-foot contact with Poole (GSW) as he is running on the perimeter.
Wiggins (GSW) swipes down and initiates contact with Lillard's (POR) arm, affecting his driving shot attempt.
Watford (POR) retracts his extended arms when marginal contact occurs with DiVincenzo (GSW), who is running toward the perimeter.
Green (GSW) dislodges the ball as he and Lillard (POR) jump toward the rebound.
DiVincenzo (GSW) is the last person to make contact with the ball before it goes out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to POR.
Watford's (POR) has a resting hand on Poole's (GSW) body as he also swipes and makes clean contact with the ball during Poole's driving shot attempt.
Thompson (GSW) places a resting forearm on Grant's (POR) side and moves alongside his path during Grant's dribble in the backcourt.
DiVincenzo (GSW) has his arm extended in Simons' (POR) path when marginal contact occurs as Simons changes direction in the backcourt.
DiVincenzo (GSW) cleanly deflects Simons' (POR) pass away prior to any incidental contact that occurs thereafter.
Wiggins (GSW) briefly grasps Simons' (POR) arm as the two engage during the rebound.
Poole (GSW) is the last person to make contact with the ball before it goes out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to POR.
Poole (GSW) commits a take foul on Payton II (POR).
Simons (POR) is the last to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. Possession correctly remains with GSW.
Simons (POR) places two hands on Poole's (GSW) side as he moves alongside Poole's path during the drive, and the contact is marginal.
Poole (GSW) attempts to commit a take foul on Simons (POR) after the expiration of the game clock.
